    • Method Detail

      • getValidTerms

        Set<OntologyTermI> getValidTerms(String accession,
                                 boolean allowChildren,
                                 boolean useTerm)
        This method builds a set of all allowed terms based on the specified parameters.
        Parameters:
        accession - the accession number of the term wanted.
        allowChildren - whether child terms are allowed.
        useTerm - whether to include the specified term ID in the set of allowed IDs.
        Returns:
        a non null set of allowed ontology terms for the specified parameters.

      • getTermForAccession

        OntologyTermI getTermForAccession(String accession)
        Search a term by accession number.
        Parameters:
        accession - the accession to be searched for.
        Returns:
        an ontology term or null if not found.
